org.cef.network

Class CefRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.network.CefRequest

  • public abstract class CefRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to represent a web request. The methods of this class may be called on any thread.(用于表示web请求的类。这个类的方法可以在任何线程上调用。)

      • getIdentifier

        public abstract long getIdentifier()
        Returns the globally unique identifier for this request or 0 if not specified. Can be used by CefRequestHandler implementations in the browser process to track a single request across multiple callbacks.(返回此请求的全局唯一标识符，如果未指定，则返回0。可以使用CefRequestHandler实现在浏览器过程中跟踪单个请求跨多个回调)

      • setHeaderByName

        public abstract void setHeaderByName(java.lang.String name,
                                     java.lang.String value,
                                     boolean overwrite)
        Set the value for the specified response header field. The Referer value cannot be set using this method.(设置指定请求头字段的值。不能使用此方法设置Referer值。)
        Parameters:
        name - The header name.(name-响应头名称。)
        value - The header value.(value-响应头值。)
        overwrite - If true any existing values will be replaced with the new value. If false any existing values will not be overwritten.(overwrite-如果为true，则任何现有值都将替换为新值。如果为false，则不会覆盖任何现有值。)
